---
title: Curried Chickpea & Cauliflower Filo Pie with Baby Leaves
description: A curry pie is the blend of two perfect warm dishes coming together to deliver us a hearty dinner. Korma curry is peppered with
chickpeas and a rich variety of veggies like cauliflower and carrot, with a golden filo pastry to hold all the delicious flavours in a
pie that will surely be gobbled up in no time.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
